  "author_association": "MEMBER",
  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "Currently `WaitForActivation` sends a rpc call through `BlockTimeByHeight` for an ETH1 block header to our attached eth1 node for each validator. This is fine if we host a few validators, however if we have a large number of validators hosted this becomes very inefficient causing a very long start up time. This issue is track the resolution of this problem. ",
